examples.en: The new treatment effected a miraculous cure.

examples.en: He made a miraculous recovery after the accident.

examples.en: Her memory is nothing short of miraculous.

examples.en: She made a miraculous recovery from her injuries.

examples.en: To the Ancients the Nile appeared almost miraculous.

examples.en: They had a miraculous escape when their car plunged into a river.

examples.en: The moral everywhere takes precedence of the miraculous.
The missionaries gave thanks to the Almighty for their miraculous deliverance from death.
